  "dailyScripture0Text": "Chomenencho, okhulupirira adzakhalamo gulu lathompho ndi nyanja, m'malo abwino pafupi ndi Mfumulizi Yamphamvu.",
  "dailyScripture0Ref": "Quran 54:54-55",
  "dailyScripture1Text": "Ndi tissindikiza iwe, O Muhammad, komanso kusiyidwa kwa ulimwengu wonse.",
  "dailyScripture1Ref": "Quran 21:107",
  "dailyScripture2Text": "Siziyo yoti Allah akwanira mu mphunziro wake? Komakaso akukulani ndi ena.",
  "dailyScripture2Ref": "Quran 39:36",
  "dailyScripture3Text": "Patuluka kuti chakuumpha ndi zabwino kwa inyo; ndi patuluka kuti chakufuna ndi zabwino lokha. Ndi Allah adzadziwa, inyo sizingadziwa.",
  "dailyScripture3Ref": "Quran 2:216",
  "dailyScripture4Text": "Chomenencho, Allah ali ndi anthu omwa mtima.",
  "dailyScripture4Ref": "Quran 2:153",
  "dailyScripture5Text": "Motero ngindikhumbukire; ine ndidzakukhumbukira inyo. Ndi ndikhumbukire, ndipo musakhumbuke.",
  "dailyScripture5Ref": "Quran 2:152",
  "dailyScripture6Text": "Chomenencho, okhulupirira kwambiri m'makumaso a Allah ndi a khalakha.",
  "dailyScripture6Ref": "Quran 49:13",
  "dailyScripture7Text": "Ndi Mkulu wanu wakutsimikiza kuti sipalimonse koma Iye, ndi kusiyidwa kwa abambo anu.",
  "dailyScripture7Ref": "Quran 17:23",
  "dailyScripture8Text": "Chonsecho, ndi kusankha kumakhala kusiyidwa.",
  "dailyScripture8Ref": "Quran 94:6",
  "dailyScripture9Text": "Ndi ali ndi inyo pomwe muli. Ndi Allah, ndi zomwe mungumiwa, akuyang'ana.",
  "dailyScripture9Ref": "Quran 57:4",
  "dailyScripture10Text": "Allah sukunakhalansi munthu kungokhala kuposa kwa iwo.",
  "dailyScripture10Ref": "Quran 2:286",
  "dailyScripture11Text": "Ndi amene akhulupira Allah — ndiye akwanira.",
  "dailyScripture11Ref": "Quran 65:3",
  "dailyScripture12Text": "Chisoni changa chibadwa zinthu zonse.",
  "dailyScripture12Ref": "Quran 7:156",
  "dailyScripture13Text": "Ndi akuti mtumizidwa anga akukuza pa mim — chomenencho ndi pafupi. Ndimayankhula pomwe amapeka.",
  "dailyScripture13Ref": "Quran 2:186",
  "dailyScripture14Text": "Amene amachita zabwino, amene ndi mamera kapena abwino, pomwe akhulupirika — titizamapeza kuti azikhala ndi moyo wabwino.",
  "dailyScripture14Ref": "Quran 16:97",
  "dailyScripture15Text": "Chomenencho, Allah sukunasintha maudwe a anthu mpaka iwo asintha zomwe ili mu mitima yawo.",
  "dailyScripture15Ref": "Quran 13:11",
  "dailyScripture16Text": "Motero musakhalapo ndipo musachedwe, ndi mudzakhala okulira ngati muli amokhulupira.",
  "dailyScripture16Ref": "Quran 3:139",
  "dailyScripture17Text": "O mtumizidwa wanga amene asinthapo ndi kusadima, musadimire chisoni cha Allah. Chomenencho, Allah amavetsa zonse.",
  "dailyScripture17Ref": "Quran 39:53",
  "dailyScripture18Text": "Ndi amene akumvetsa Allah — iye akumanga njira yake, ndi kumapatsa kwa kumapeza zomwe sanafunanso.",
  "dailyScripture18Ref": "Quran 65:2-3",
  "dailyScripture19Text": "Musadimire chisoni cha Allah.",
  "dailyScripture19Ref": "Quran 12:87",
  "dailyScripture20Text": "Ndi tatengeza Quran kuti ibwino kukhumbuka. Ine pali amene adzalingalira?",
  "dailyScripture20Ref": "Quran 54:17",
  "dailyScripture21Text": "Ndi wakupeza inyo mochedwa ndi akukugidani.",
  "dailyScripture21Ref": "Quran 93:7",
  "dailyScripture22Text": "Ndi Mkulu wanu akuti pepani kwa ine; ndimayankhula.",
  "dailyScripture22Ref": "Quran 40:60",
  "dailyScripture23Text": "Ndi tatengeza mthamanga wa ana a Adam.",
  "dailyScripture23Ref": "Quran 17:70",
  "dailyScripture24Text": "Ndi pezani thandizo mwa kumwa mtima ndi mapipila.",
  "dailyScripture24Ref": "Quran 2:45",
  "dailyScripture25Text": "Amene amachita zinthu zaatomu koma zabwino adzaziwona.",
  "dailyScripture25Ref": "Quran 99:7",
  "dailyScripture26Text": "Chomenencho, thandizo la Allah ndi pafupi.",
  "dailyScripture26Ref": "Quran 2:214",
  "dailyScripture27Text": "Ndi amene akusiyidwa — kusiyidwa kwake kumapindula kuchokera iyeyo.",
  "dailyScripture27Ref": "Quran 31:12",

  "dailyReflection0": "Pomaliza nthawi yanu, lingalirani mphindi imodzi pomwe chisoni cha Allah cinawonekeka.",
  "dailyReflection1": "Kalatani kwa Allah chilichonse chomwe chipegeza mtima wanu.",
  "dailyReflection2": "Dzani kusiyidwa kumodzi kukhonokho ndi kusiyidwa kwa Allah.",
  "dailyReflection3": "Phumulirani mumadziwa kuti munasungidwa mu chikondi cha Allah.",
  "dailyReflection4": "Lingalirani pomwe mukumutumidwa kuwonetsa chisoni ndi chitimbire.",
  "dailyReflection5": "Letani zimene simungathandize ndi kutenga mtima kwa cholinga chabwino cha Allah.",
  "dailyReflection6": "Pomaliza nthawi, mundani mtendere mwa Dhikr ya Allah.",
  "dailyReflection7": "Lingalirani momwe munalekedeza mapipila anu ndi kusiyidwa kwa Allah.",
  "dailyReflection8": "Lingalirani mphindi pomwe kumwa mtima kwakugidani zanu.",
  "dailyReflection9": "Mufunirani mwankhoswe kwa zinthu zosiyiliza — chisoni cha Allah sichimathe.",
  "dailyReflection10": "Dzani munthu amodzi yemwe mumwonesetsa chisoni ndi pemirani.",
  "dailyReflection11": "Khulupirit kusiyidwa: chani chomwe Allah chinakupatsa komwe sinakufunike?",
  "dailyReflection12": "Lingalirani ayi a Quran yomwe ikutanthauza kumene muli.",
  "dailyReflection13": "Lingalirani momwe mugwiritsa nthawi yanu — ndi kumsowezetsa Allah nthawi yatsopano.",
  "dailyReflection14": "Phumulirani mumadziwa kuti pangano lero, Allah anali nanu.",
  "dailyReflection15": "Lingalirani njira imodzi yomwe munakothira banja kapena chilamulo lero.",
  "dailyReflection16": "Pomaliza nthawi, pepani Tawbah — Allah amakonda amene amabuwerera.",
  "dailyReflection17": "Lingalirani abwino a Allah omwe adapachila.",
  "dailyReflection18": "Lingalirani zomwe munaziphunzira ndi momwe zimakutalikitsani kwa Allah.",
  "dailyReflection19": "Letani nkhawa za nthawi ndi Allah — iye amakhumatula zomwe simungathandize.",
  "dailyReflection20": "Lingalirani mphindi komwe munatha kukhala abwino, ndi kuphunzira.",
  "dailyReflection21": "Pemirani anthu omwe akuvutika — pepani yanu ndi mphatso yawo.",
  "dailyReflection22": "Khumbukira kusiyidwa komwe simungankhumbuk ndi kusiyidwa kwa Allah.",
  "dailyReflection23": "Lingalirani zolinga zanu — ankale za Allah? Nthawi yatsopano, yambani chatsopano.",
  "dailyReflection24": "Pomaliza nthawi, dumphani kwa Allah — ali pafupi.",
  "dailyReflection25": "Lingalirani pomwe mwapeza mphamvu — mphamvu iyi imangokhala ndiyakwa Allah.",
  "dailyReflection26": "Dzani chinthu chimodzi chomwe munzachita bumaiyoni kwa Allah.",
  "dailyReflection27": "Polamula kuphunzira, sowezetsan mzimu wanu kwa Allah — iye ndiye wachilungamo.",

