  "disclaimerTitle": "Pa umvekedwe wa app inu",
  "disclaimerBody": "Nuria imapatsa kulingalira koona ka Islamic, kukhumbukira, ndi zokumbukira za chromu kuti zithandize njira yanu ya chikhulupiriro. Zinthu izi zimapatsidwa kwa cholinga cha mfundo za wamba ndi ndondomeko.\n\nNuria siimaloweza mwachiphunzitso.\nNdondomeko mu app inu siimaloweza kwa mlalendo wakuphunzitsa, imam, mufti, kapena waphunzitso wachikhulupiriro. Ngati muli ndi mafunso pa zolawa za Islamic, zinthu zolipiliro, kapena zodziwika zachikhulupiriro, pezani ndondomeko kwa waphunzitso wakuphunzitsa mu chilamulo chanu.\n\nApp inu simakupatsa zolawa zachikhulupiriro.\nNuria siikupereka zomwe zimadzifuna pa fiqh (Islamic jurisprudence) kapena zodziwika zachikhulupiriro. Zinthu zolanda siziyenera kuganiziridwa monga fatwa kapena zolawa zachikhulupiriro.\n\nMaphunziro asintha.\nIslam imaphatikiza nthano yabwino ya nthano, amalamulo (madhabs), ndi mawonekedwe a mlalendo. Zokumbukira mu app inu zikuwonetsa mawonekedwe awamba komanso zingathe kusiyanasiyana pa nthano iliyonse.\n\nChilamulo chinachimachita.\nApp inu idzakonzekera kuzamilamula mu nthano ya chikhulupiriro pomwe ikulekarsa gawo lolitsa la mosque yanu, imam, ndi anthu anzanu okhulupirira. Tinachimachita kuti mukhale ndi ubale ndi kuti muphunzire kwa waphunzitso akuphunzitsa pafupi.",
  "disclaimerClose": "Ndamvetsa",
  "disclaimerInfoTooltip": "Pa umvekedwe wa app inu",
  "disclaimerSettingsSubtitle": "Kwa cholinga cha mfundo za wamba okha. Dina kuti muwerenge zolemba zonse.",
  "disclaimerSectionHeader": "Kumvekedwera kwa ndondomeko"
}